The Service will be for the provision of a complete solution up to involvement of a Pathologist, this means the interested party is responsible for providing and funding the provision of associated assets (i.e. any equipment (a CT Scanner or MRI Scanner) and any necessary buildings to house the equipment and perform the services), general running costs (i.e. utilities, maintenance, etc.), any necessary software for performing the main function of the contract, as well as the sourcing, and/or employment (including pay rolling, or other payment mechanisms compliant with IR35 rules) of necessary personnel, this should include as a minimum Radiographers and Radiologists, and may need to include porters, cleaners, and other labourers and workers necessary for performing the contract.

